New_Bedford.Dartmouth High School (Massachusetts):
Dartmouth High School is a four-year public high school located in Dartmouth, Massachusetts, United States.
As of the 2016/17 school year, the school had an enrollment of 1,064 students and 78.4 classroom teachers (on an FTE basis), for a student-teacher ratio of 13.6.


== History ==
The school began in 1902 on Russell's Mills Road in what is now the Salt-Marsh Pottery.
